      *                  * Prompts per prima pagina testata            *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           perform   pmt-tes-reg-000      thru pmt-tes-reg-999        .
           move      "#"                  to   w-cnt-sts-pmt-ptx
                                              (w-cnt-sts-imp-npt)     .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Video in 'ON'                               *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           move      "ON"                 to   v-ope                  .
           call      "swd/mod/prg/obj/mvideo"
                                         using v                      .
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Tipo impostazione : chiave                      *
