      *                      * diato                                   *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           if        w-tes-cod-cbp-cge (1)
                                          not  = zero
                     go to acc-cod-cbp-475.
           if        w-tes-cod-cbp (1)    =    spaces
                     go to acc-cod-cbp-475.
