      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Video in Off                                    *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      "OF"                 to   v-ope                  .
           call      "swd/mod/prg/obj/mvideo"
                                         using v                      .
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Visualizzazione testata registrazione           *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           perform   vis-tes-reg-000      thru vis-tes-reg-999        .
