      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      "SV"                 to   v-ope                  .
           call      "swd/mod/prg/obj/mvideo"
                                         using v                      .
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Video in Off                                    *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
