      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Literal per 'Messaggio'                         *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      "DS"                 to   v-ope                  .
           move      "A"                  to   v-tip                  .
           move      12                   to   v-car                  .
           move      12                   to   v-lin                  .
           move      03                   to   v-pos                  .
           move      "Messaggio  :"       to   v-alf                  .
           call      "swd/mod/prg/obj/mvideo"
                                         using v                      .
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
