      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      "DS"                 to   v-ope                  .
           move      "A"                  to   v-tip                  .
           move      63                   to   v-car                  .
           move      12                   to   v-lin                  .
           move      16                   to   v-pos                  .
           move      "La presentazione distinta non viene pertanto esegu
      -              "ita.         "      to   v-alf                  .
